{"tid":469434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國安徽特大連環車禍  18人死亡21人受傷","createTime":"2017-11-15T10:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T11:07:30.000Z","uid":141461,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb1519380a5630ae9cdea3293bef21e3cd34fc0","tid":469434,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:07:47.000Z","msg":"阜陽市委宣傳部官方微博最新通報，目前，滁新高速事故共造成18人死亡，21名傷者現在醫院救治，其中傷勢較重11人<br />\n<br />\n安徽省阜陽市公安局交警支隊通報，2017年11月15日7時45分許，在&ldquo;滁新高速&rdquo;下行線191KM至194KM路段，因突發團霧，發生多點多起造成人員傷亡的交通事故。<br />\n<br />\n事故發生後，當地政府迅速組織公安，消防，交通，安監，醫療等部門全力開展事故救援和調查工作。省市縣有關領導現場調度指揮救援處置工作。<br />\n<br />\n目前，事故共造成18人死亡，21名傷者現在醫院救治，其中傷勢較重11人"},{"pid":"ccd442a076c8aa86fa588615bc09ee5818d560b6","tid":469434,"uid":85163,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:08:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7748cf07338046c4588e93bdc905f5a7723da95f","tid":469434,"uid":141461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31d944595752eef222864416443152b80027ca0","tid":469434,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74d5eed0946dca2823437f91dd77cb2af2cbcad","tid":469434,"uid":9348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:26:08.000Z","msg":"死咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1796635eb2db89a2094443640d21b821f2b5ba37","tid":469434,"uid":45657,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T10:27:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n死得少？<br />\n<br />\n佢地會繼續努力 再創佳績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003383b48aee43a3